text.section:
The Department shall issue a renewal certificate of registration if the Department determines that:
all required documents have been filed and are satisfactory;
any revised agreements for continuing care at home services meet the Department's requirements;
the proposed use of new or existing health facilities is not inconsistent with the State health plan;
the provider has submitted all proposed advertisements, advertising campaigns, and other promotional materials for the program; and
the form and substance of all advertisements, advertising campaigns, and other promotional materials submitted are not deceptive, misleading, or likely to mislead.
